# team.info

返回当前团队信息。

## 请求方式

```
GET {base_url}/team.info
```

## 请求参数

**需要登录**


## 响应

### 200

```json
{
  "id": "=bw52O",
  "subdomain": "openapi",
  "name": "BearyChat OpenAPI",
  "email_domain": null,
  "logo_url": null,
  "description": "",
  "plan": "basic",
  "created": "2017-01-11T12:28:31.000+0000"
}
```
### 错误响应

```json
{
  "code": // error code,
  "error": "unexpected error"
}
```
